'''Isaiah Vagana''' (born 14 June 2000) is a New Zealand  professional [[rugby league]] [[footballer]] who plays as a {{rlp|sr}} for [[Wakefield Trinity]] in the [[Super League]].

==Background==
Isaiah is the son of former [[Bradford Bulls]] {{rlp|pr}} [[Joe Vagana]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/rugby-league/articles/cvgl8n7lzglo |title=Wakefield forward Vagana signs new three year deal |publisher=BBC Sport |date=6 November 2024}}</ref>

==Career==
===2025===
Vagana made his debut in round 1 of the [[2025 Super League season]] for Trinity against the [[Leeds Rhinos]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.superleague.co.uk/match-centre/report/43416 |title=Super League Match Report |publisher=Super League |date=15 February 2025}}</ref>

